---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | The Açai Club" description="How The Açai Club collects & uses your personal data.">

  <section class="pt-28 pb-24 bg-dark min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">

      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-4">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-grey text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none space-y-8 text-grey leading-relaxed">

        <p>
          We, the legal owner of The Açai Club, understand that your privacy is important to you & that you care about how your personal data is used & shared online. We respect & value the privacy of everyone who visits this website & will only collect & use personal data in ways that are described here, & in a manner that is consistent with our obligations & your rights under the law.
        </p>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            The Açai Club is a food & beverage business operating stores in Reading, Beaconsfield, & Datchet, UK. Our registered address is 10a High Street, Datchet, United Kingdom SL3 9EA.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Our online ordering system is operated by EPoS Technologies Limited, whose registered office is 11 Wharf Road, Enfield, EN3 4TA, Middlesex, United Kingdom.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">2. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>As a data subject under the UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Be informed about how we collect & use your personal data</li>
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Rectification of inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
            <li>Erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
            <li>Restrict or object to processing of your data</li>
            <li>Data portability</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you have a complaint about how we handle your data, you may contact the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-beige hover:text-light transition-colors">ico.org.uk</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">3. What Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>Depending on how you use our site & services, we may collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Name, email address, & telephone number</li>
            <li>Delivery or billing address (when placing orders)</li>
            <li>Order history & preferences</li>
            <li>IP address, browser type, & operating system</li>
            <li>Usage data (pages visited, time on site)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Payment information is processed securely by Stripe & is never stored on our systems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">4. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p>We use your data to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Process & fulfil your orders</li>
            <li>Manage your loyalty rewards account</li>
            <li>Send order confirmations & service updates</li>
            <li>Respond to enquiries</li>
            <li>Improve our website & services</li>
            <li>Send marketing communications (only with your consent)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience. Strictly necessary cookies ensure the site works as intended. We may also use analytics cookies (e.g. Google Analytics) to understand how visitors use the site. You can control cookie settings through your browser at any time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">6. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell your personal data. We may share it with trusted third-party service providers (such as our ordering platform, payment processor Stripe, & email service providers) solely to operate our business. All processors are bound by appropriate data processing agreements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes it was collected, or as required by law. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            For any questions about this Privacy Policy or to exercise your data rights, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 space-y-1">
            <p>The Açai Club</p>
            <p>10a High Street, Datchet, United Kingdom SL3 9EA</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@theacaiclub.com" class="text-beige hover:text-light transition-colors">hello@theacaiclub.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-light mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. We recommend checking this page periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
